prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: Two months ago, I was named the head of a new project at the work place. The position came with higher pay. This made me pay off my debt. I was so happy because of this. I celebrated by going to a fancy restaurant. I got some queso to start off the meal. The queso was very yummy. I got some beers to drink. They were nice to drink. I got a steak as the main meal. The steak was medium. It was one of the best steaks I have ever eaten. I got a nice chocolate cake for dessert. I gave the waiter a big tip. I can't wait to begin working on the new project. It should be fun. I have a lot of ideas for the project.
